Summary of important user-visible changes for Bio-Root
------------------------------------------------------

{{$NEXT}}
  * First release as an independent distribution, after split from bioperl-live.
  * Bio::Root::Root
    - Support of Clone::Fast as a faster cloning alternative [fangly]
  * Bio::Root::IO
    - Moved the format() and variant() methods from Bio::*IO modules to
      Bio::Root::IO [fangly]
    - Can now use format() to get the type of IO format in use [fangly]
    - More reliable detection of mode() and support for streams opened in
      read+write mode [fangly]
    - file() now reports filename and mode in array context
